# AI Agent – Environment Variables
#
# ─── AUTH PRIORITY ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only ONE of these setups is needed:
#
#   Option A (recommended):  GITHUB_COPILOT_TOKEN alone
#   Option B (direct APIs):  ANTHROPIC_KEY + OPENAI_KEY
#
# Copilot-first: your Copilot token covers Claude + GPT models.
# If you also set ANTHROPIC_KEY or OPENAI_KEY they take priority
# for that provider (useful for dedicated billing / higher limits).
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# HOW TO GET YOUR COPILOT TOKEN:
#   Option 1:  gh auth token            (if you have GitHub CLI)
#   Option 2:  https://github.com/settings/tokens → Classic → copy
#
# HOW TO GET DIRECT API KEYS (optional):
#   Anthropic:  https://console.anthropic.com → API Keys → Create Key
#   OpenAI:     https://platform.openai.com   → API Keys → Create New

# ─── REQUIRED (pick one option) ────────────────────────────────────────
GITHUB_COPILOT_TOKEN=gho_your-copilot-token-here

# ─── OPTIONAL OVERRIDES ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ANTHROPIC_KEY=sk-ant-your-claude-api-key-here
# OPENAI_KEY=sk-your-gpt-api-key-here
